## Installation

- **Using `pip`**

```bash
pip install shortiepy
```

## Usage

- **Add a URL**

```bash
shortiepy add https://example.com
```

- **Start server**

```bash
shortiepy serve  # will run in forground
# OR
shortiepy start  # will run in background
```

- **View docs**

```bash
shortiepy docs
```

